&lt;iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/223414827" width="640" height="360" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://vimeo.com/223414827"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href="https://vimeo.com/user58915964"&gt;劉育彤&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href="https://vimeo.com"&gt;Vimeo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><category term="Ubuntu"></category><category term="Putty"></category></entry><entry><title>期末考週</title><link href="./2017spring-wcm-final.html" rel="alternate"></link><published>2017-06-18T12:00:00+08:00</published><updated>2017-06-18T12:00:00+08:00</updated><author><name>yen</name></author><id>tag:,2017-06-18:./2017spring-wcm-final.html</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;以下為網際內容管理 2017 Spring 第十八週學員連結.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;!-- 導入 Brython 標準程式庫 --&gt;

